paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: Extracted information on the KCNH2 gene variant rs35760656, including clinical significance, penetrance data, and individual records.

patients.demographics: Hispanic/Latino ancestry, predominantly female (64%), middle-aged (mean age 49 years)

functional_data.summary: Strong experimental evidence for transcriptional activation in heart tissue.

variants.additional_notes: The variant was identified in a GWAS of QT interval in Hispanic/Latino populations.

tables_processed.table_caption: Genome-wide significant loci identified in a GWAS meta-analysis of n = 15,997 participants of Hispanic/Latino ancestry from four studies, that were previously reported.

extraction_metadata.notes: Only one variant in the KCNH2 gene was reported in the paper.
